'''Ōtoshi Shrine''' (大歳神社) is a {{ill|Shinto Shrine|ja|神社}} located in {{ill|Kinokawa City, Wakayama Prefecture|ja|紀の川市}}, Japan.

== Deities ==
The main deities enshrined at the shrine are {{ill|Ōichi-hime no Mikoto|ja|神大市比売}}, {{ill|Shibahara Myōjin|ja|芝原明神}}, and {{ill|Wakamiya Hachiman Shrine|ja|若宮八幡宮}}.

