ing| religious_affiliation = [[Shinto]] |name = Ōtoshi Shrine | religious_affiliation = [[Shinto]] |image = {{image requested|cat=Kinokawa City}} |location = {{ill|Kinokawa City, Wakayama Prefecture|ja|紀の川市}}, Momoyama-chō Tsukizuki 1110 |coordinates = {{coord|34|13|39.3|N|135|19|51.1|E|region:JP-30_type:landmark|display=inline,title}} |deity = {{ill|Kamuo Ichihime|lt=Ōichi-hime no Mikoto|ja|神大市比売}}, {{ill|Shibahara Myōjin|ja|芝原明神}}, {{ill|Wakamiya Hachiman Shrine|ja|若宮八幡宮}} |Main Hall = Wooden |Map = {{location map|Japan Wakayama Prefecture|label=Ōtoshi Shrine|float=center|relief=1|width=256}} }} '''Ōtoshi Shrine''' (大歳神社) is a {{ill|Shinto Shrine|ja|神社}} located in {{ill|Kinokawa City, Wakayama Prefecture|ja|紀の川市}}, Japan.
